        <div class="cc-faq-body"><div class="cc-faq-body__inner"><div class="cc-faq-answer">After artwork approval, production takes 4–8 weeks depending on edition size. We send you a production sample first (2 weeks). Once approved, full production runs in batches and we begin selling as inventory is ready.</div></div></div>
