        <div class="cc-faq-body"><div class="cc-faq-body__inner"><div class="cc-faq-answer">Yes, within a range. Public editions are priced between $80–$250 per piece. We agree on the price together based on edition size, artwork, and positioning. Your 70% commission applies to the agreed sale price.</div></div></div>
