        <div class="cc-faq-body"><div class="cc-faq-body__inner"><div class="cc-faq-answer">For public editions, unsold inventory is held by IRIS with no cost to you. We may run targeted promotions to sell remaining pieces. You earn your commission on every piece sold, whenever it sells. There's no deadline pressure on your end.</div></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cc-faq-item">
        <button class="cc-faq-toggle" type="button"><span class="cc-faq-question">Do I retain rights to my artwork?</span><span class="cc-faq-plus">+</span></button>
